9
00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:03,160
♪ Sweat illuminating in the hot sun ♪

10
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:05,680
♪ Dear youth ♪

11
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:07,000
♪ Dear youth ♪

12
00:01:07,080 --> 00:01:10,160
♪ Keep running, your dreams lie ahead ♪

13
00:01:10,239 --> 00:01:12,720
♪ Dear youth ♪

14
00:01:12,800 --> 00:01:14,040
♪ Dear youth ♪

15
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:17,120
♪ Don't be afraid, work hard and grow up ♪

16
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:20,760
♪ We are in the best years of youth ♪

17
