♪ Live the way ♪

19
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:32,440
♪ You want to live the most ♪

20
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:42,960
The Prince of Tennis
~ Match! Tennis Juniors! ~

21
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:48,000
[tense music]

22
00:01:51,520 --> 00:01:52,560
[man gasps]

23
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,680
JI JINGWU, XING YAO HIGH SCHOOL,
CAPTAIN

24
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:58,160
You said it was a doubles match.

25
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,680
Why aren't you playing?

26
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:04,280
[grunts]

27
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:10,039
[Xing Zi] Are you Ji Jingwu from Xing Yao?

28
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,400
My name is Xu Xing Zi.
I'm from Yu Feng High School.

29
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:14,039
We'll be your opponent in the next game.

30
00:02:14,479 --> 00:02:15,360
[sucks teeth]

31
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:17,280
Any school...

32
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:20,880
can play in regionals nowadays?

33
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:23,240
The game hasn't started yet,
and yet you're already judging.

34
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:25,040
I'm just telling the truth.

35
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:27,040
[Jingwu] I can tell
if you are qualified...

36
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:29,800
or not.

37
00:02:29,880 --> 00:02:32,440
Don't go too far.
What's your problem with Xing Yao?

38
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,240
Strength is not measured by words.

39
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:35,360
You dare...
[gasps]

40
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:37,440
So, you want to play against me?

41
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,160
Stop it!

42
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:42,080
Let her go.

43
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,520
You're lucky...

44
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:50,560
to get help so quickly.

45
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:53,440
Let me take care of them.

46
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,840
[Jingwu exhales sharply]

47
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:02,800
But they are formidable. Can you do it?

48
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:04,560
Have you ever seen me playing tennis?

49
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:07,600
Mm-hm.

50
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,440
You stay away from her.

51
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,120
Yu Qing boy.

52
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:16,760
[Weiming] What is your name?

53
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:18,680
Can you play doubles?

54
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,000
There are two of them.

55
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:23,600
I'll say it just once. Remember...

56
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:27,440
I am Qiao Chen from Yu Qing.

57
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,480
I'm the best doubles player.

58
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:37,120
[comical music]

59
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:40,560
Can you really play the net game?

60
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:43,600
I can do anything
as long as you don't hold me back.

61
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:47,240
You can serve first.

62
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:49,200
It's an all-or-nothing game.

63
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:51,360
Find your own position.

64
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,760
Chonghong.

65
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,240
Okay.

66
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,560
[upbeat music]

67
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:12,840
Are you kidding me? One-on-two?

68
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,200
[Qiao Chen] You underestimate us.

69
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:16,680
[Weiming] Be careful.

70
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:24,399
[thwacks]

71
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:26,200
[grunts]

72
00:04:26,839 --> 00:04:27,680
[Qiao Chen] Damn.

73
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:29,280
[Weiming] Can you really play doubles?

74
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:30,240
[grunts]

75
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:33,640
Chonghong.

76
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:35,560
[whooshes]

77
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:37,480
He can run fast.

78
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,080
[Qiao Chen] I got this.

79
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,840
Vertical smash.

80
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:45,960
Chonghong, return the ball.

81
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:50,960
[grunts]

82
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:54,640
Qiao Chen.

83
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:56,240
[exhales sharply]

84
00:04:58,720 --> 00:04:59,880
[sighs]

85
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:01,960
[Qiao Chen groans]

86
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,440
[Jingwu] Stop.

87
00:05:07,240 --> 00:05:09,880
-[sighs sharply]
-Who are you again?

88
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:11,200
Qiao Chen, form Yu Qing.

89
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:14,040
Why? Are you afraid of me?

90
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,240
Yu Qing?

91
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:16,200
[Qiao Chen snickers]

92
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:18,200
[sighs]

93
00:05:18,800 --> 00:05:20,200
Say hello to Siyang for me.

94
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,760
Hey.

95
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:25,320
I'm Shen Weiming from Yu Feng.

96
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,800
-No one is asking.
-[chuckles]

97
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:30,720
I...

98
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:43,240
Thank you, guys.

99
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:45,080
You're welcome.

100
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:50,880
Uh, you still owe me one.
You left your phone in the classroom.

101
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:52,920
I came here to return it to you.

102
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:55,440
-[Weiming] Hm.
-[chuckles]

103
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:57,880
Thank you. Silly me. I forgot about it.

104
00:05:57,960 --> 00:05:58,840
It's okay.

105
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:04,080
So, you just came to return the phone?

106
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:07,480
Why did you ask me who I was?
Is this your business?

107
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,800
You...

108
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,840
What's the matter?

109
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,240
I thought you were friends.

110
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:15,000
[both] No way.

111
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:18,920
[Mu] I'm warning you, don't take it.

112
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,840
I am not a frightening person,
but I am terrifying when I get angry.

113
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:22,240
[Xiuwen] This is too much.

114
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:24,640
I don't know what to do.

115
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:26,760
I can only pay the bill.

116
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:30,320
What will they do
when they meet at the crossroads?

117
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:34,280
How about settling the problem in a game?

118
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:36,760
[Mu] Huh?

119
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:38,960
Hmm, good idea.

120
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,800
[somber music]

121
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,440
[doctor] Mu Siyang.

122
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:06,080
Here's the examination report
regarding your arm injury.

123
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,160
[sighs]

124
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:41,320
[PA announcement]
We are arriving at Tao Yuan Cun Station.

125
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:42,520
[sighs]

126
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:45,160
We seldom take the subway together.

127
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:50,040
You seem to be bothered.

128
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:59,440
[doctor] The initial examination shows
your elbow condition is not stable.

129
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:02,000
And it may be further deteriorated.

130
00:08:03,280 --> 00:08:07,160
The rehabilitation made some progress,
but it's important to rest well.

131
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:10,760
I know, you have to consider
a lot of things.

132
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,480
I can help you.

133
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,760
[PA announcement]
We are arriving at Feng Shan Station.

134
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,440
[exhales sharply]

135
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:27,720
If we have to elect a new captain,

136
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,880
who do you think is the best candidate?

137
00:08:30,560 --> 00:08:32,200
Is this what you want to talk about?

138
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:40,000
Isn't it too early
to consider the candidate?

139
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:42,640
[phone ringing]

140
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:48,600
Coach.

141
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:54,400
[whirring]

142
00:08:57,640 --> 00:08:59,080
[beeping]

143
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:05,360
XING YAO HIGH SCHOOL

144
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:07,840
[phone beeps]

145
00:09:09,080 --> 00:09:10,040
ACCEPT

146
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,840
I'VE ACCEPTED YOUR FRIEND REQUEST

147
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,080
[Yan Zhiming] You are...

148
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:15,120
[man 1] If I don't tell you who I am,

149
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:17,160
there's a 50-percent chance
that you know me,

150
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:19,040
and a 50-percent chance that you don't.

151
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:22,720
So I will confuse you
by not letting you know who I am.

152
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:28,560
[teacher] All right. I've written
the solution on the blackboard.

153
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:29,760
Take a good look at it.

154
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:32,800
You can discuss it with each other.

155
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:35,880
-The math teacher praised me again.
-Yes.

156
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,240
He said I made much progress.

157
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:41,040
9 DAYS BEFORE MUNICIPAL QUALIFYING

158
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:43,880
[Siyang] There are only nine days
before the municipal qualifying.

159
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:46,720
We'll start our special training today.

160
00:09:47,560 --> 00:09:50,080
We'll practice rallies in a limited range.

161
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:52,040
Which means to practice in a certain area.

162
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:54,480
-Yan.
-Hm.

163
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:56,640
[Yan Zhiming]
Let's do a five-ball rally exercise.

164
00:09:57,040 --> 00:10:00,760
I will divide you into four groups
according to your shot style.

165
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:04,160
Hold-and-attack defense players
and serve-and-volley players

166
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:06,360
can only attack half court.

167
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:11,280
Aggressive-attack and all-court players
must defend the whole court.

168
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:14,240
If one can't score within five returns,

169
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,800
it's a loss by default.

170
00:10:15,880 --> 00:10:17,600
The attacking players can only win

171
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:20,120
if they can score
within five balls, right?

172
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,320
Right.

173
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:23,040
So the defenders win

174
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:25,040
if they can successfully return
five shots.

175
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,080
Mm-hm.

176
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,240
Huh?

177
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:30,960
That sounds like fun.

178
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:33,760
If the ball touches the net
or falls in the wrong area,

179
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,120
the player loses immediately.

180
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:36,680
Mm-hm.

181
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:40,160
Losers have to...

182
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:42,480
drink this cup of Yan-juice.

183
00:10:43,280 --> 00:10:45,280
[comical music]

184
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:49,320
[nervous chuckle]

185
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:52,600
That doesn't sound fun at all.

186
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:53,720
[Tang Jiale chuckles]

187
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:56,680
[Peng] Your aunt must be happy.

188
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:59,640
We have so many talented players now.

189
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:01,960
Even an ignored player like Xinglong

190
00:11:02,360 --> 00:11:05,280
can change a lot in the game.

191
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,640
Baiyang, too.

192
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:08,800
He seems tough,

193
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:11,520
but he's reliable at the vital moment.

194
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:15,440
Half-court or all-court,
it makes no difference.

195
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:16,760
[gasps]

196
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:19,920
-Good shot.
-Bad shot! He Xinglong won.

197
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:21,560
[sighs]

198
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:26,160
Trust me, you'll be stronger.

199
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:28,720
[stutters]

200
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:31,800
He never shows his weakness.

201
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:34,600
[Baiyang groaning]

202
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:36,600
It's too bitter.

203
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:39,080
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

204
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:40,880
[Dayong] Moon-volley.

205
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:43,120
MOON-VOLLEY

206
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,160
[gasps]

207
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:47,800
-[sighs]
-[Yan Zhiming] Qiao Chen won.

208
00:11:47,880 --> 00:11:48,880
Yeah!

209
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:55,960
-[sighs]
-And Dayong is really gentle.

210
00:11:56,520 --> 00:11:58,600
I always feel good when he's with us.

211
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:01,280
[Dayong] It's too bitter.

212
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:03,040
[Baiyang] It's too bitter.

213
00:12:03,680 --> 00:12:04,800
[breathing heavily]

214
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,560
-[grunts]
-[thwacks]

215
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:08,960
[snickers]

216
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:11,560
[Yan Zhiming] Bad shot. Jiale won.

217
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:14,960
[Ying] Lu Xia.

218
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:17,560
He never holds back

219
00:12:18,160 --> 00:12:19,720
whatever difficulties he comes across.

220
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:23,000
-[Baiyang] It's too bitter.
-[Dayong] It's too bitter.

221
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,160
[chuckles]

222
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:29,720
-[Dayong] The bitterness is gone.
-[Coach Qi] Siyang.

223
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:30,680
[Dayong groans]

224
00:12:30,760 --> 00:12:33,080
[Coach Qi] The result of the
qualifying is here.

225
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:36,520
The passing schools are good.

226
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,520
But...

227
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:40,520
only four of them
can get in the next round.

228
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:44,720
Yu Feng will play against Xing Yao
before we do.

229
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:50,960
We have to beat our opponents
before meeting our greatest enemies.

230
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:55,320
Yes, we aim to win
the national championship.

231
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:57,640
[Coach Qi] All right, dismissed.

232
00:13:09,800 --> 00:13:11,040
-Auntie.
-Yes.

233
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:14,000
We agreed to go at 2:00 tomorrow, right?

234
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,280
Oh.

235
00:13:15,640 --> 00:13:16,840
I forgot about it.

236
00:13:16,920 --> 00:13:18,200
[Coach Qi] I can't make it.

237
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:19,680
I have another appointment.

238
00:13:20,160 --> 00:13:24,000
Ahh. I'll have to fix the racket
on my own?

239
00:13:24,800 --> 00:13:28,880
But I don't know much
about fixing a tennis racket.

240
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:30,160
Wait a minute.

241
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:33,200
[sighs]

242
00:13:36,680 --> 00:13:37,640
Lu Xia.

243
00:13:38,560 --> 00:13:40,200
-Are you available tomorrow?
-Yes.

244
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:44,000
Okay. Can you accompany Ying
to have her racket fixed?

245
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,040
Huh?

246
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,200
Hmm.

247
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,360
[gulps]

248
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:50,440
-[water trickling]
-[crickets chirping]

249
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:57,720
[tense music]

250
00:14:04,160 --> 00:14:05,760
Do you have any plans for tomorrow?

251
00:14:05,840 --> 00:14:06,840
Yes.

252
00:14:07,760 --> 00:14:09,440
[Lu Xia] Let's play a game
when I come back.

253
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:16,320
Don't stay with me all the time, okay?

254
00:14:16,400 --> 00:14:19,400
You can go out, make some friends
and walk your cat.

255
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:20,960
I'm not interested.

256
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:23,400
What are you interested in?

257
00:14:23,480 --> 00:14:24,400
Beating you.

258
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:27,880
And after that?

259
00:14:31,160 --> 00:14:33,720
Just forget it. I will not play seriously.

260
00:14:35,040 --> 00:14:35,920
Why?

261
00:14:37,920 --> 00:14:39,120
I...

262
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:42,960
I can't play when I'm hungry.

263
00:14:43,800 --> 00:14:45,600
[Xiangqian chuckles]
How about this?

264
00:14:46,040 --> 00:14:48,640
I heard the roasted goose
from the corner is good.

265
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,640
Buy me some.

266
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:52,840
No, buy it yourself.

267
00:14:52,920 --> 00:14:54,160
Fine, fine, fine.

268
00:14:54,920 --> 00:14:56,840
Play tennis by yourself, too.

269
00:14:58,840 --> 00:14:59,800
[inhales deeply]

270
00:15:05,560 --> 00:15:07,120
[chuckles]

271
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:19,160
YU QING WINS!

272
00:15:20,800 --> 00:15:22,800
[somber music]

273
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:28,800
[inhales sharply]

274
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,080
[Xiangqian] Brat.

275
00:15:44,960 --> 00:15:46,120
Besides tennis,

276
00:15:46,520 --> 00:15:49,800
the most meaningful thing in life
is these sweet memories.

277
00:15:53,560 --> 00:15:55,320
Thank you for coming. Bye.

278
00:15:56,640 --> 00:15:57,880
-Is it yummy?
-[woman 1] Yes.

279
00:15:58,880 --> 00:15:59,760
Hi, sir.

280
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:01,840
-Are you here for Xinglong?
-Yes.

281
00:16:02,280 --> 00:16:04,120
Come in, he is inside.

282
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:08,840
[Lu Xia] Xinglong.

283
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:12,800
Lu Xia, why are you here?

284
00:16:12,880 --> 00:16:13,880
To buy some goose.

285
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:17,480
Oh. Wait a minute.

286
00:16:18,280 --> 00:16:19,960
[indistinct chatter]

287
00:16:24,880 --> 00:16:25,960
-[sighs]
-[utensils clinking]

288
00:16:26,040 --> 00:16:28,000
Do you help out here all the time?

289
00:16:28,080 --> 00:16:28,960
Yes.

290
00:16:29,560 --> 00:16:33,000
By the way, just text me
anytime you want some goose.

291
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:34,480
You can come get it when it's ready.

292
00:16:34,560 --> 00:16:35,400
Okay?

293
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:36,600
[chuckles]

294
00:16:36,680 --> 00:16:38,960
[Lu Xia] You practice tennis
and help your father every day.

295
00:16:39,040 --> 00:16:40,160
It's tough, right?

296
00:16:41,480 --> 00:16:44,680
Why? Doing your favorite things
would never be hard.

297
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:48,120
I love cooking and playing tennis.

298
00:16:49,040 --> 00:16:50,040
[Lu Xia] Favorite things?

299
00:16:50,480 --> 00:16:51,440
But...

300
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:54,160
I don't know how long
I can keep doing them...

301
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:55,680
at the same time.

302
00:16:57,280 --> 00:17:00,600
-Xinglong, I'll get their orders ready.
-Okay, Dad.

303
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:03,920
Lu Xia, wait a minute. I'll be back soon.

304
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:05,160
Mm-hm.

305
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:09,400
[light music]

306
00:17:10,200 --> 00:17:11,359
[He Xinglong panting]

307
00:17:11,440 --> 00:17:13,119
[Lu Xia] I should not bother him.

308
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,240
-Please.
-[woman 2] Thank you.

309
00:17:15,319 --> 00:17:16,160
It's good.

310
00:17:21,160 --> 00:17:23,319
-[Mr. He] The goose is ready.
-[He Xinglong] I'm coming.

311
00:17:27,280 --> 00:17:29,520
[breathes heavily]

312
00:17:34,160 --> 00:17:36,720
[Young Lu Xia]
Dad, you're such a good tennis player.

313
00:17:36,800 --> 00:17:38,440
I want to play with you.

314
00:17:39,040 --> 00:17:41,760
[Xiangqian] You'll be better than Daddy
when you grow up.

315
00:17:48,840 --> 00:17:49,920
[soft chuckle]

316
00:17:51,680 --> 00:17:52,560
Lu Xia.

317
00:17:54,560 --> 00:17:56,200
Sorry for making you wait so long.

318
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,120
Here's the goose.

319
00:17:58,480 --> 00:18:01,360
-I will give you one more tomorrow.
-Thank you.

320
00:18:02,840 --> 00:18:04,200
It's late.

321
00:18:04,600 --> 00:18:07,720
-Let me walk you home. I'm going out.
-Where are you going?

322
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:11,600
To practice.
I don't have much time during the day.

323
00:18:12,800 --> 00:18:13,640
Practice?

324
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:15,480
Yes.

325
00:18:16,360 --> 00:18:18,680
Do you want to come with me?

326
00:18:18,760 --> 00:18:20,440
-Uh-huh.
-Let's go.

327
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:25,160
[He Xinglong] You left your goose.

328
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:27,040
[Lu Xia] I'll come for it later
after practice.

329
00:18:27,160 --> 00:18:29,360
[thwacking]

330
00:18:31,080 --> 00:18:32,920
-[thwacks]
-[He Xinglong grunts]

331
00:18:36,920 --> 00:18:38,000
Burning!

332
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:48,920
Lu Xia.

333
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:50,480
Huh...

334
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,200
Get some rest.

335
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:54,040
[He Xinglong pants]

336
00:18:56,520 --> 00:18:57,560
[groans]

337
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:00,640
Mmm.

338
00:19:03,800 --> 00:19:04,720
[sighs]

339
00:19:04,800 --> 00:19:08,440
You practice every day
after working at the restaurant.

340
00:19:08,720 --> 00:19:09,680
Mm-hm.

341
00:19:10,280 --> 00:19:11,480
It's busy at the restaurant.

342
00:19:11,560 --> 00:19:14,800
So I practice every second I can.

343
00:19:15,920 --> 00:19:18,440
What's more, the match is coming up.

344
00:19:18,520 --> 00:19:19,760
I want to practice more.

345
00:19:20,320 --> 00:19:21,800
I don't want to be a burden.

346
00:19:23,800 --> 00:19:25,440
Thank you for practicing with me.

347
00:19:25,520 --> 00:19:26,960
I always practice alone.

348
00:19:27,320 --> 00:19:28,480
I rarely feel this excited.

349
00:19:28,560 --> 00:19:32,080
You can't do rallies when you're alone,
but you can if you play with others.

350
00:19:32,160 --> 00:19:33,280
[chuckles]

351
00:19:33,760 --> 00:19:34,840
And not just that.

352
00:19:34,920 --> 00:19:36,920
I was practicing alone all the time.

353
00:19:37,640 --> 00:19:40,280
I worked really hard
on some unique skills.

354
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:42,480
I felt good about myself.

355
00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:46,160
Then I entered the club
and practiced with others.

356
00:19:46,840 --> 00:19:48,800
[He Xinglong] I realized
those skills are useless.

357
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:49,880
[chuckles]

358
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:54,560
But they couldn't handle the strength
I was already used to.

359
00:19:56,120 --> 00:19:57,400
[groans]

360
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:58,440
Xinglong.

361
00:20:03,960 --> 00:20:05,040
[grunts]

362
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:08,280
The coach's advice and the other players

363
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:11,520
made me a stronger player.

364
00:20:12,040 --> 00:20:15,480
Otherwise, I would still be
practicing my unique skills here.

365
00:20:15,560 --> 00:20:16,520
[chuckles]

366
00:20:17,880 --> 00:20:20,760
Anyway, two is better than one.

367
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:24,560
We can help each other
and find each other's weaknesses.

368
00:20:25,880 --> 00:20:26,920
I just...

369
00:20:27,600 --> 00:20:29,240
want to play tennis with everyone.

370
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:31,440
So I always...

371
00:20:32,000 --> 00:20:35,280
want to be on the court
and win the game for us.

372
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:37,120
For us?

373
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:38,840
[panting]

374
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:46,800
[soft chuckle]

375
00:20:48,040 --> 00:20:51,040
Do you think playing with me is helpful?

376
00:20:51,120 --> 00:20:54,000
Sure. I rarely play with strong players.

377
00:20:54,320 --> 00:20:55,480
[gasps]

378
00:20:56,440 --> 00:20:59,640
We can practice together
if you don't mind.

379
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:01,880
Great. I would like to ask...

380
00:21:01,960 --> 00:21:04,440
-Uh-huh?
-why do you play tennis?

381
00:21:05,320 --> 00:21:06,400
"Why"?

382
00:21:07,720 --> 00:21:09,880
There's no reason. I just enjoy it.

383
00:21:13,800 --> 00:21:14,800
Enjoy it?

384
00:21:19,760 --> 00:21:21,160
[stomach grumbles]

385
00:21:22,960 --> 00:21:25,520
[He Xinglong] I'm sorry,
you didn't have your supper.

386
00:21:25,600 --> 00:21:27,360
Don't mind it. Tennis comes first.

387
00:21:28,560 --> 00:21:29,760
[He Xinglong] Try this.

388
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:31,600
[He Xinglong chuckles]

389
00:21:35,080 --> 00:21:37,080
[comical music]

390
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:44,280
[sighs]

391
00:21:48,040 --> 00:21:48,960
What do you think?

392
00:21:49,320 --> 00:21:50,360
[groans]

393
00:21:50,440 --> 00:21:51,680
Burning.

394
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:01,320
What took you so long?

395
00:22:03,240 --> 00:22:04,200
Lu Xia,

396
00:22:04,280 --> 00:22:07,920
my father cooks better than me.

397
00:22:08,280 --> 00:22:10,720
He teaches me how to cook.

398
00:22:10,800 --> 00:22:12,360
Will you run a restaurant in the future?

399
00:22:12,800 --> 00:22:14,760
[He Xinglong chuckles]
Take your time.

400
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:18,760
It was a small store when my father
took it over from my grandpa.

401
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:22,720
I saw him do all the work.

402
00:22:23,080 --> 00:22:24,120
Gradually,

403
00:22:24,560 --> 00:22:29,040
he developed that small store
into this big restaurant.

404
00:22:30,600 --> 00:22:33,240
He named me after the restaurant.
[chuckles]

405
00:22:33,320 --> 00:22:34,720
Do you admire your father?

406
00:22:35,120 --> 00:22:36,040
Yes.

407
00:22:36,360 --> 00:22:39,240
I'll be like him.
I'll be a wonderful cook.

408
00:22:42,160 --> 00:22:43,800
You should do better than him.

409
00:22:44,120 --> 00:22:45,120
Mm-hm.

410
00:22:45,520 --> 00:22:48,080
I will do better than my father, too.

411
00:22:48,360 --> 00:22:49,200
[sniffs]

412
00:22:50,760 --> 00:22:54,880
Does the brat know his old man
is crying miserably for food?

413
00:22:55,960 --> 00:22:58,400
Does your father also play tennis?

414
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:02,680
Yes, but he never plays with me seriously.

415
00:23:04,120 --> 00:23:04,960
[soft chuckle]

416
00:23:05,400 --> 00:23:07,360
You are lucky to have
someone to play with.

417
00:23:07,720 --> 00:23:09,640
I really hope to beat him someday.

418
00:23:12,960 --> 00:23:15,120
Is your father that great?

419
00:23:17,920 --> 00:23:19,920
[comical music]

420
00:23:24,280 --> 00:23:25,920
I'm starving.

421
00:23:31,520 --> 00:23:35,360
8 DAYS BEFORE MUNICIPAL QUALIFYING

422
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:40,440
[soft chuckle]

423
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:43,400
[light music]

424
00:23:56,560 --> 00:23:59,360
[woman 3] Ying, aren't you going
to get your racket fixed?

425
00:23:59,440 --> 00:24:00,560
Why are you making a cake?

426
00:24:00,960 --> 00:24:05,160
I'm making this to thank the one
who's going with me to fix my racket.

427
00:24:06,560 --> 00:24:08,400
[woman 3] Who is he?
That cake is too much.

428
00:24:09,800 --> 00:24:12,360
Oh, damn. I'm not finished yet.

429
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:14,960
I'll be late.

430
00:24:20,960 --> 00:24:22,760
Hey, where are you going?

431
00:24:23,280 --> 00:24:24,120
Buy me two crullers

432
00:24:24,200 --> 00:24:27,440
and a cup of soy milk
with two spoonsful of sugar.

433
00:24:27,520 --> 00:24:28,400
I'm in a hurry.

434
00:24:29,280 --> 00:24:31,480
Just buy them on your way.
Don't be so mean.

435
00:24:31,560 --> 00:24:32,600
I have an appointment.

436
00:24:33,560 --> 00:24:34,400
An appointment?

437
00:24:35,920 --> 00:24:36,760
[sighs]

438
00:24:36,840 --> 00:24:37,760
You?

439
00:24:38,080 --> 00:24:39,040
It's not like you.

440
00:24:39,120 --> 00:24:40,120
Someone asked me out.

441
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:41,800
Who? A boy or a girl?

442
00:24:42,440 --> 00:24:43,360
It's Qi Ying.

443
00:24:43,680 --> 00:24:44,920
Whoa!
[chuckles]

444
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:47,920
Qi Na's niece, right?
I'm in favor of that girl.

445
00:24:49,160 --> 00:24:51,080
I'm meeting with her
to get her racket fixed.

446
00:24:51,800 --> 00:24:52,960
Hey, son.

447
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:56,200
You are too young to fall in love.

448
00:24:56,280 --> 00:24:57,840
-Studying comes first.
-[cat meows]

449
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:01,440
This is for you.

450
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:06,160
[cat meows]

451
00:25:11,360 --> 00:25:12,760
Here it is.

452
00:25:14,160 --> 00:25:16,200
Dad, wash this.

453
00:25:24,440 --> 00:25:26,600
Brat, how can you order me around?

454
00:25:35,920 --> 00:25:37,240
It's hand embroidered.

455
00:25:40,600 --> 00:25:42,640
Is he going on a date?

456
00:25:43,760 --> 00:25:45,440
[Ying panting]

457
00:25:55,640 --> 00:25:58,160
Hello! Chief, I have an idea.

458
00:25:58,600 --> 00:26:02,680
We have to start with Lu Xiangqian
if we want to find a breakthrough.

459
00:26:03,360 --> 00:26:07,280
I understand, but you know,
he is quite stubborn.

460
00:26:07,760 --> 00:26:10,120
The magazines you gave are not enough.

461
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:11,960
Let's figure something out.

462
00:26:13,120 --> 00:26:14,040
Hello?

463
00:26:14,440 --> 00:26:15,360
Chief?

464
00:26:16,760 --> 00:26:19,920
[sighs]
Can I have some good luck?

465
00:26:21,600 --> 00:26:22,480
-[grunts]
-[gasps]

466
00:26:22,560 --> 00:26:23,440
My god.

467
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:25,360
I'm sorry. Are you okay?

468
00:26:25,680 --> 00:26:27,200
What are you doing here?

469
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:30,560
I shouldn't have made this cake.

470
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:32,360
Get up. Are you okay?

471
00:26:32,440 --> 00:26:34,200
-Come on.
-I'm fine.

472
00:26:34,280 --> 00:26:36,840
Are you going on a date?

473
00:26:37,160 --> 00:26:41,000
Uh, no. I'm just meeting someone
to have my racket fixed.

474
00:26:41,080 --> 00:26:43,560
I made this cake to thank him.

475
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:45,440
Thank Lu Xia?

476
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:49,480
I'm sorry, Sha. I'm late. I have to go.

477
00:26:49,560 --> 00:26:51,040
-Take care.
-[Ying] Mm-hm. Bye.

478
00:26:52,840 --> 00:26:53,920
[sighs]

479
00:27:05,920 --> 00:27:07,160
Lu Xiangqian?

480
00:27:07,600 --> 00:27:08,560
[car horn honks]

481
00:27:09,240 --> 00:27:10,280
[exhales sharply]

482
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:13,560
I can't stop thinking about him.
It's taken over my mind.

483
00:27:17,640 --> 00:27:19,840
[panting]

484
00:27:22,320 --> 00:27:24,800
-Sorry, I'm late.
-Let's go.

485
00:27:29,320 --> 00:27:31,320
[somber music]

486
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:36,480
Okay. Can you accompany Ying
to have her racket fixed?

487
00:27:36,560 --> 00:27:37,600
Huh?

488
00:27:38,280 --> 00:27:40,120
[Ying] Am I troubling him?

489
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:44,120
He seems hesitant to go with me.

490
00:27:45,080 --> 00:27:46,520
And I was late.

491
00:27:50,560 --> 00:27:52,360
I shouldn't have made that cake.

492
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:02,520
She's only 20 minutes late.

493
00:28:03,440 --> 00:28:04,920
Why are you so angry?

494
00:28:06,200 --> 00:28:07,760
She is just a little girl.

495
00:28:09,520 --> 00:28:11,120
[Xiangqian] I must keep an eye on you.

496
00:28:12,560 --> 00:28:14,320
Don't fall in love so early.

497
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:20,560
QIAO CHEN FROM YU QING IS OFF LIMITS

498
00:28:23,440 --> 00:28:26,040
[staff] Sir, you have to pay if you
can't finish within ten minutes.

499
00:28:26,120 --> 00:28:26,960
[groans]

500
00:28:27,480 --> 00:28:28,560
[retches]

501
00:28:29,040 --> 00:28:30,840
[man 2] You're right. I can't eat anymore.

502
00:28:30,920 --> 00:28:32,120
-[man 2 groaning]
-[staff] Okay.

503
00:28:32,200 --> 00:28:33,120
[Qiao Chen burps]

504
00:28:33,600 --> 00:28:35,800
[staff 2] He is a big eater
like Qiao Chen.

505
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:38,800
He ate eleven hamburgers
in less than five minutes.

506
00:28:38,880 --> 00:28:39,720
[phone ringing]

507
00:28:39,800 --> 00:28:43,080
-[staff] Sir, take your time.
-[man 2] Call a cab for me.

508
00:28:44,920 --> 00:28:48,480
Hello, I'm on my way.
I will be there soon.

509
00:28:48,560 --> 00:28:49,960
[Baiyang] Are you still eating?

510
00:28:51,480 --> 00:28:54,520
No. You misheard me.
[burps]

511
00:28:54,600 --> 00:28:57,080
[Baiyang] Hello. Why are you still eating?

512
00:28:57,960 --> 00:28:59,200
It's getting dark.

513
00:28:59,560 --> 00:29:01,040
[Qiao Chen] It's...

514
00:29:02,080 --> 00:29:03,920
I'm coming soon.

515
00:29:05,760 --> 00:29:07,240
[comical music]

516
00:29:07,320 --> 00:29:10,160
You again.
You can't fool me with a mustache.

517
00:29:11,280 --> 00:29:12,520
I made it, so it's a free meal.

518
00:29:13,240 --> 00:29:14,800
Don't come back again!

519
00:29:16,960 --> 00:29:18,960
[playful music]

520
00:29:22,640 --> 00:29:23,600
[Qiao Chen] Sir!

521
00:29:24,760 --> 00:29:25,680
Sir!

522
00:29:26,560 --> 00:29:27,400
Qiao Chen.

523
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:30,440
-[mumbles]
-What are you doing here?

524
00:29:31,960 --> 00:29:34,080
-Are you following Lu Xia?
-I...

525
00:29:42,320 --> 00:29:44,760
[breathing heavily]

526
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:51,640
[sighs]
It's too close.

527
00:29:51,720 --> 00:29:52,680
Yes.

528
00:29:53,200 --> 00:29:54,400
Take this.

529
00:29:55,400 --> 00:29:56,400
I'm going.

530
00:29:58,040 --> 00:29:59,040
Sir!

531
00:30:01,200 --> 00:30:02,120
Baiyang.

532
00:30:02,360 --> 00:30:03,360
Why are you here?

533
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:04,400
Look at your phone.

534
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:12,880
Stop talking. I lost him.

535
00:30:13,560 --> 00:30:15,120
Lost who?

536
00:30:16,840 --> 00:30:18,600
Hey. Hey!

537
00:30:23,640 --> 00:30:25,640
[suspenseful music]

538
00:30:30,000 --> 00:30:31,960
[Ying] There is a bookstore.

539
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:35,600
I don't think
we can get the racket fixed here.

540
00:30:36,600 --> 00:30:38,720
We can. You just don't see it.

541
00:30:41,160 --> 00:30:43,160
[playful music]

542
00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:56,840
Keep quiet.

543
00:31:00,600 --> 00:31:03,080
Something is fishy between them.

544
00:31:03,160 --> 00:31:06,000
I promised I would take care of Lu Xia.

545
00:31:06,520 --> 00:31:08,440
He must study hard,
not to develop a relationship.

546
00:31:09,080 --> 00:31:10,040
Go.

547
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:20,760
The shopkeeper is not in.

548
00:31:24,760 --> 00:31:25,680
Lu Xia.

549
00:31:33,360 --> 00:31:34,680
[Lu Xia] What are you looking for?

550
00:31:43,200 --> 00:31:44,160
[sighs]

551
00:31:45,560 --> 00:31:48,040
I didn't know there was such a place.

552
00:31:48,680 --> 00:31:49,920
How did you find it?

553
00:31:50,320 --> 00:31:52,200
Go in. I'll wait outside.

554
00:31:53,040 --> 00:31:55,160
-[Jiang] Aren't you coming to visit me?
-[Lu Xia grunts]

555
00:31:56,120 --> 00:31:56,960
[gasps]

556
00:31:58,440 --> 00:32:00,680
-Uncle Jiang.
-What a rare visitor.

557
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:03,040
Where is your father?

558
00:32:03,760 --> 00:32:05,720
-She wants to get her racket fixed.
-[soft chuckle]

559
00:32:05,800 --> 00:32:07,480
Hi, sir. My name is Qi Ying.

560
00:32:07,840 --> 00:32:08,720
Qi Ying?

561
00:32:09,360 --> 00:32:10,600
Is Qi Na your...

562
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:13,160
Do you know my auntie?

563
00:32:13,520 --> 00:32:17,440
Yes. I fix your auntie's rackets
and Lu Xiangqian's rackets too.

564
00:32:17,520 --> 00:32:18,880
As well as Lu Xia's rackets.

565
00:32:19,160 --> 00:32:20,440
They're all unbeatable players.

566
00:32:20,920 --> 00:32:22,560
I should take credit for them.

567
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:23,920
I'm not unbeatable.

568
00:32:24,240 --> 00:32:26,480
Isn't he unbeatable?
[chuckles]

569
00:32:27,800 --> 00:32:29,040
Yes, he is.

570
00:32:30,280 --> 00:32:31,400
Let's get to the point.

571
00:32:42,000 --> 00:32:44,280
Sir, please help me fix it.

572
00:32:45,600 --> 00:32:48,600
I can tell from the strings
that you practiced a lot.

573
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,080
I'll take care of it.

574
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:51,720
Thank you.

575
00:32:51,800 --> 00:32:54,440
Uncle, be quick. I have something to do.

576
00:32:54,520 --> 00:32:57,040
Take it easy. You can watch TV here.

577
00:33:06,080 --> 00:33:07,360
[soft chuckle]

578
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:18,760
-[thwacking]
-[squeaking]

579
00:33:27,360 --> 00:33:29,640
Why are you replaying
this game all the time?

580
00:33:30,760 --> 00:33:33,240
It's the peak of Lu Xiangqian's career.

581
00:33:34,120 --> 00:33:35,640
[Jiang] Every hit was perfect.

582
00:33:36,280 --> 00:33:37,120
Really?

583
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:40,440
It's a pity that he retired so early.

584
00:33:40,880 --> 00:33:44,360
[Jiang] No one has broken his record
of a 37-match winning streak.

585
00:33:46,360 --> 00:33:49,040
LU XIANGQIAN

586
00:33:50,840 --> 00:33:53,520
Is he your father?

587
00:33:53,840 --> 00:33:54,720
Are you done?

588
00:33:55,120 --> 00:33:56,080
Not yet. Take it easy.

589
00:33:56,800 --> 00:33:58,720
[Jiang] Keep watching your father's game.

590
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:00,040
He was brilliant.

591
00:34:00,800 --> 00:34:02,160
[Lu Xia] I will do better than him.

592
00:34:04,360 --> 00:34:05,440
[gasps]

593
00:34:06,680 --> 00:34:08,159
Why did you turn it off?

594
00:34:11,840 --> 00:34:13,120
[snickers, sighs]

595
00:34:16,520 --> 00:34:19,600
[Ying] Lu Xia, your father is awesome.

596
00:34:19,679 --> 00:34:20,600
He is awesome, I know.

597
00:34:21,880 --> 00:34:26,280
You must be very proud
to have such a great dad.

598
00:34:26,719 --> 00:34:28,159
[Lu Xia] I want to be his pride, too.

599
00:34:31,840 --> 00:34:32,960
[snickers]

600
00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:44,679
Jiale, this is serious. You have to come.

601
00:34:54,320 --> 00:34:56,320
[upbeat music]

602
00:35:00,880 --> 00:35:01,800
[scoffs]

603
00:35:02,720 --> 00:35:03,640
[sighs]

604
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:08,400
[comical music]

605
00:35:19,840 --> 00:35:21,240
It's true.

606
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:24,240
Why are you so sneaky?

607
00:35:24,320 --> 00:35:28,840
That boy dares to walk
with a girl in public.

608
00:35:28,920 --> 00:35:29,800
[Baiyang] Lu Xia?

609
00:35:33,920 --> 00:35:35,480
I don't think he means it.

610
00:35:39,440 --> 00:35:40,480
[both gasp]

611
00:35:41,960 --> 00:35:44,040
Don't be too close to me.

612
00:35:44,640 --> 00:35:46,600
No, you're too close to me.

613
00:35:46,680 --> 00:35:48,120
[groans, gasps]

614
00:35:52,200 --> 00:35:54,200
[playful music]

615
00:36:13,320 --> 00:36:14,600
Finally.

616
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:16,520
I'm tired.

617
00:36:19,360 --> 00:36:20,480
[grunts]

618
00:36:21,840 --> 00:36:23,400
[groaning]

619
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:41,320
-Is that for me?
-Mm-hm.

620
00:36:41,600 --> 00:36:42,600
Let's eat it together.

621
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:44,960
Mm-hm.

622
00:37:02,560 --> 00:37:05,040
I'm so sorry.

623
00:37:06,040 --> 00:37:10,600
I made this cake
to thank you for coming with me.

624
00:37:11,240 --> 00:37:14,400
But I had an accident on my way.

625
00:37:16,320 --> 00:37:18,320
[romantic music]

626
00:37:23,680 --> 00:37:24,680
It tastes good.

627
00:37:27,080 --> 00:37:29,000
[soft chuckle]

628
00:37:33,360 --> 00:37:34,760
[chuckles]

629
00:37:36,440 --> 00:37:37,520
[car horn honks]

630
00:37:47,080 --> 00:37:48,080
[Xiuwen] Jing.

631
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:52,680
I'm still not finished with my homework.
Why did you ask me to come?

632
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:54,120
You know nothing.

633
00:37:54,880 --> 00:37:57,000
He humiliated me at the beginning.

634
00:37:57,600 --> 00:38:00,280
If I can prove to the school
that he is dating a girl,

635
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:02,640
then he has to quit the tennis club.

636
00:38:02,720 --> 00:38:04,800
And then I can be a first-team player.

637
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:08,320
You are so evil.

638
00:38:13,160 --> 00:38:15,160
[playful music]

639
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:18,320
[both gasp]

640
00:38:19,440 --> 00:38:21,520
Aren't you repairing the stretcher
in the hospital?

641
00:38:21,600 --> 00:38:23,200
What are you doing here?

642
00:38:24,120 --> 00:38:25,560
Qiao Chen.

643
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:28,000
We got lost.

644
00:38:28,080 --> 00:38:32,440
I'm warning you. I won't let you off
if Lu Xia quits the nationals

645
00:38:32,520 --> 00:38:34,240
because of some accident.

646
00:38:34,320 --> 00:38:36,640
-[Qiao Chen] Right, Baiyang?
-I agree.

647
00:38:39,840 --> 00:38:41,880
You two are bullying my son?

648
00:38:42,200 --> 00:38:46,320
No, sir. We are concerned about him.

649
00:38:46,400 --> 00:38:48,000
We have no guts to bully him.

650
00:38:48,080 --> 00:38:51,080
Yes, we serve him
delectable food and drink.

651
00:38:51,720 --> 00:38:52,560
Right.

652
00:38:52,640 --> 00:38:56,040
We can't enter the first-team,
we can only hang around the stretcher.

653
00:38:56,120 --> 00:38:58,360
We even start feeling uncomfortable...

654
00:38:58,920 --> 00:39:00,280
without it.

655
00:39:00,360 --> 00:39:03,520
Every time I see two iron poles
with a piece of cloth,

656
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:05,920
we can't help but take it.

657
00:39:06,360 --> 00:39:09,520
Our neighbors came to talk to my family

658
00:39:09,880 --> 00:39:13,880
and asked us not to steal their sheets,
blankets, and clothes.

659
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:15,880
Life is not easy, right?

660
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:17,680
Yes, isn't life hard enough for us?

661
00:39:18,720 --> 00:39:19,600
[exhales sharply]

662
00:39:19,920 --> 00:39:23,000
Yes, you two really work hard.
We misunderstood you.

663
00:39:23,400 --> 00:39:24,320
Mmm.

664
00:39:25,800 --> 00:39:27,840
[panting]

665
00:39:28,200 --> 00:39:30,360
Uh, hello, sir, I'm Lu Xia's classmate.

666
00:39:30,440 --> 00:39:31,920
Hello.

667
00:39:33,240 --> 00:39:35,600
You guys are not acting
the way Yu Qing students usually do.

668
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:37,400
Sir, don't worry.

669
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:40,280
Lu Xia won't become a bad student
on our watch.

670
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:41,640
Oh.
[chuckles]

671
00:39:41,720 --> 00:39:43,360
Sir, I just keep spying on them.

672
00:39:43,440 --> 00:39:45,480
Fine, go on.

673
00:39:46,120 --> 00:39:47,200
Aha.

674
00:39:48,560 --> 00:39:49,440
[chuckles]

675
00:39:51,400 --> 00:39:52,760
[Tang Jiale chuckling]

676
00:39:52,840 --> 00:39:55,240
We are concerned about Lu Xia, too.
How can we miss this?

677
00:39:55,320 --> 00:39:57,160
They can't have puppy love.

678
00:39:58,320 --> 00:40:00,080
-Hello, I'm Lu Xia's father.
-I'm Zhuo Zhi.

679
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:03,800
-Hi, nice to meet you.
-Hi, sir, it's a pleasure to meet you.

680
00:40:04,640 --> 00:40:07,120
Shouldn't we look at that?

681
00:40:18,600 --> 00:40:20,120
You just came back from abroad.

682
00:40:20,480 --> 00:40:23,480
The teachers asked me
to help you review the lessons.

683
00:40:24,040 --> 00:40:27,160
But I don't know much about you.

684
00:40:28,200 --> 00:40:31,840
And it seems that you don't want to talk
about your father.

685
00:40:32,760 --> 00:40:36,400
I can understand why you don't.
There must be a lot of pressure

686
00:40:36,680 --> 00:40:38,680
when you want to surpass
your father's achievements.

687
00:40:38,760 --> 00:40:40,160
Why do you suddenly talk about this?

688
00:40:42,680 --> 00:40:44,960
[stuttering]
Because...

689
00:40:46,640 --> 00:40:48,560
-Because--
-You talked too much today.

690
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:51,800
[somber music]

691
00:40:52,560 --> 00:40:53,680
[sighs]

692
00:40:56,240 --> 00:40:57,200
[breathing heavily]

693
00:40:58,720 --> 00:40:59,920
What's the matter?

694
00:41:00,160 --> 00:41:01,880
[Qiao Chen] Does he really like Ying?

695
00:41:02,480 --> 00:41:03,320
It can't be.

696
00:41:03,400 --> 00:41:06,080
-He must focus on his studies.
-Right.

697
00:41:11,400 --> 00:41:16,200
Thank you for coming with me today.
I'm going to get the racket myself.

698
00:41:28,440 --> 00:41:30,400
[bird chirping]

699
00:41:36,920 --> 00:41:41,080
Hey, Siyang, it's Sunday.
Why are you here?

700
00:41:41,520 --> 00:41:43,360
-Coach.
-Take a seat.

701
00:41:49,280 --> 00:41:51,520
Coach, I want to have a game with Lu Xia.

702
00:41:52,440 --> 00:41:56,040
But the competition will start soon.

703
00:41:56,680 --> 00:41:57,680
I know.

704
00:41:58,560 --> 00:42:00,120
Are you sure?

705
00:42:00,760 --> 00:42:02,280
I mean, it's a critical moment.

706
00:42:02,960 --> 00:42:03,800
Mmm.

707
00:42:04,720 --> 00:42:06,760
[exhales sharply]

708
00:42:07,320 --> 00:42:09,640
Give me a good reason for that.

709
00:42:10,360 --> 00:42:13,200
I have to do this.

